org.apache.oodt.cas.cli.util

Class CmdLineIterable<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.oodt.cas.cli.util.CmdLineIterable<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<T>

    public class CmdLineIterable<T>
extends Object
implements Iterable<T>
    An Iterable which allows multiple concurrent iterators which affect each other, also allows you to increment iterators index manually. All iterators handle termination safely. However, the catch being that you can only iterate through this Iterable once, then you must create a new object of it to iterate over it again.
    Author:
    bfoster (Brian Foster)
